sentence.text: Six genes (ACOX2, DNA damage response, signal transduction by p53 class mediator resulting in cell cycle arrest, visual perception, PSPH, sterol biosynthetic process, TYMS) were differentially expressed by race among Luminal A breast cancers and were associated with survival (HR <0.8, HR >1.25).
